Class NamespaceMap

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.apache.lenya.util.NamespaceMap
public class NamespaceMap
extends java.lang.Object

An object of this class provides an easy way to access Strings in a Map that are prefixed like "prefix.foo".

Author:
Andreas Hartmann
